        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Foster Care Stabilization Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Administration for Children and Families to award demonstration grants to foster care stabilization agencies to improve services for foster youth awaiting placement and for other emergency assistance.</p>]]>
        </text>
